This project is a card display built using **Next.js** and **Tailwind CSS**. It dynamically presents student information with smooth hover effects. The cards scale up and reveal a black shadow when hovered, enhancing the user experience. Tailwind's utility-first approach has been used to implement custom transitions, transformations, and shadows.

## Features:
- Responsive design with Tailwind CSS
- Smooth hover effect with a 1.5s transition
- Scale-up effect with shadow on hover
- Built with modern web technologies (Next.js & Tailwind CSS)

## Tech Stack:
- Next.js (React framework)
- Tailwind CSS (Utility-first CSS framework)

Feel free to explore the project and leave feedback!

